parameters:
There's clean water accumulated here. I should be able to
wash off the dirt from my body.
Would you like to wash off the dirt from your body?
\n<Man>"Oh...? Could you possibly be Lady Roselitte?"

\n<Man>"My apologies for the intrusion. I am Benji, a merchant from
Annabern."

\n<Benji>"Due to the recent attack, there's a shortage of medical
supplies and many other goods, isn't there? It's bad for
business. That's why I'm personally gathering ingredients
for medicine."

\n<Benji>"Many refugees are falling ill in these unfamiliar
conditions. I must do business, even if it's a bit reckless,
for their sake and mine. Hahaha."

\n<Ameria>"Medicine would be a great help! There are many who need
continuous treatment."

\n<Benji>"Oh, you are... I remember now. You're the young healer who
was treating people in the square, right? You've been a
great help. It's hard to see people suffering."
Benji narrowed his eyes as he looked at Ameria.

\n<Benji>"If everyone could be treated by such a lovely healer, they
would surely be delighted."
\n<Ameria>"Ehehe... Lovely, you say? Oh, I don't know about that..."

\n<Benji>"...Right, Lady Roselitte. I hope I'm not overstepping my
bounds, but I have a suggestion."

\n<Benji>"As I mentioned earlier, the town is running low on
supplies. Most shops are closed, and you must be having
trouble on your travels as well."

\n<Benji>"So here's an idea. If you would listen to a request from
me, I could offer you supplies at a discounted price."
\n<Roselitte>"Hmm... that would be helpful, but... what is this request?"
\n<Benji>"As expected of Lady Roselitte, quick to discern."

\n<Benji>"It's nothing difficult. When you return to town, I would
like to borrow the young healer for a while."

\n<Benji>"So her name is Ameria. Yes, that's right. I would like to
borrow her assistance for a short time."

\n<Benji>"Due to my profession, I have dealings with many partners.
Many of them are in trouble because of the recent attacks.
With Ameria's help, they would surely be grateful."

\n<Ameria>"If my help is needed, of course I'll do it! But I want to
prioritize you, Roselitte-san, so within what I can manage."
\n<Benji>"Wonderful. Of course, only when you can spare the time."

\n<Benji>"I'll be in the square just to the left as you enter town.
Please call on me when you're ready to lend your strength.
We can discuss business then."
